data.description: Beautiful home close to parks, shopping, restaurants and schools. Traditional 3 bed/2.5 bath home with an office. The open main floor plan invites cozy entertainment and holiday gatherings in front of the fireplace. The fenced in backyard and covered concrete patio offers you a  open area to become the undefeated neighborhood grillmaster. Upstairs you'll find the spacious master bedroom with private bath and walk-in closet. A full bath and two other spacious bedrooms! Move in ready!
